      <h1>GLC <span>PRESS CLUB</span></h1>
      <p>Empowering students to communicate confidently — through journalism, broadcasting, and leadership. Your story starts here.</p>
      <a href="#membership" class="btn">✎ Join the Press Club</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- About -->
  <section id="about" class="section-white">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>About the club</h2>
      <p class="about-text">We help students develop real‑world speaking skills, journalistic integrity, and the confidence to present news in front of large audiences. Through teamwork, creativity, and leadership, our members become the voice of the school.</p>
      <div class="card-grid" style="margin-top: 2.5rem;">
        <div class="card"><i class="fas fa-microphone-alt"></i><h3>Public speaking</h3><p>Weekly speaking drills, anchoring, and stage presence training.</p></div>
        <div class="card"><i class="fas fa-pen-fancy"></i><h3>Journalism</h3><p>Report writing, interviewing, and editing school news.</p></div>
        <div class="card"><i class="fas fa-users"></i><h3>Teamwork</h3><p>Collaborative projects, from news casting to event coverage.</p></div>
        <div class="card"><i class="fas fa-crown"></i><h3>Leadership</h3><p>Take charge as editors, anchors, and club officers.</p></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Activities -->
  <section id="activities" class="section-light">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Our activities</h2>
      <div class="card-grid">
        <div class="card"><i class="fas fa-video"></i><h3>News casting</h3><p>Live morning announcements and assembly news segments.</p></div>
        <div class="card"><i class="fas fa-user-tie"></i><h3>Interviews</h3><p>Interview teachers, students, and special guests.</p></div>
        <div class="card"><i class="fas fa-newspaper"></i><h3>School reporting</h3><p>Write articles for the school blog and monthly magazine.</p></div>
        <div class="card"><i class="fas fa-camera-retro"></i><h3>Event coverage</h3><p>Media coverage of sports day, cultural fests, and more.</p></div>
        <div class="card"><i class="fas fa-comments"></i><h3>Debate & speech</h3><p>Practice impromptu speaking and structured debates.</p></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- EXECUTIVES -->
